<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta http-equiv="x-ua-compatible" content="ie=edge">
  <title>Welcome Email</title>

  <style>
    .mails-body {
        font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace !important;
        color: black !important;
        font-size: 16px;
    }
    .btn {
        background-color: black;
        height: 3rem;
        cursor: pointer;
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 1rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        padding-inline: 3rem;
    }
    a {
        color: white !important;
        text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="mails-body">
        <h3>Hi {{name}}, </h3>
        <p>You recently requested to reset the password for your {{company}} account. Click the button below to proceed.</p>
        <button type="button" class="btn"><a href={{linkUrl}}>Reset Password</a></button>
        <p>If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email or reply to let us know. This password reset link is only valid for the next 30 minutes.</p>
        <h4>Thanks, the {{company}} support team</h4>
    </div>
</body>
</html>